# Implementation Plan - ShipSync (AI Courier Billing & Excel Automation)

ShipSync is a premium AI-powered logistics SaaS application that automates courier billing, consignment segregation, and OCR-based parcel document extraction. It provides a stunning dashboard, a high-performance billing calculator, custom zone/weight slab managers, and powerful Excel export features.

---

## User Review Required

We are designing this application with high premium standards, including dynamic glassmorphism, animated transitions (Framer Motion), charts (Recharts), and a unified project launcher. 

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Database Strategy:** To enable a **zero-configuration local run** immediately, we will use **SQLite** as the default database for Prisma. Prisma makes it trivial to swap to **PostgreSQL** (just changing the provider in `schema.prisma` and updating the database URL in `.env`). We will provide full documentation and a PostgreSQL schema file for production deployment.
>
> **OCR Pipeline:** We will use **Tesseract.js** in the backend Node environment. Tesseract.js is a pure JavaScript OCR engine. It requires **no native binaries or complex Tesseract software installations on Windows**, which avoids permission and compatibility issues, and executes OCR flawlessly on your local PC.
>
> **Fuzzy Name Matching:** We will implement the Levenshtein distance algorithm combined with token sorting to accurately map variations like `"Alfred Pvt Ltd"`, `"ALFRED"`, and `"Alfred Company"` to a canonical company name.

