#### [NEW] [schema.prisma](file:///c:/Users/sandh/OneDrive/Documents/exspenso/Desktop/ShipSync/backend/prisma/schema.prisma)
- **Database Schema**:
  - `User`: Admin/Employee login records.
  - `Company`: Consolidated company listings with fuzzy name alias maps.
