#### [NEW] [fuzzyMatcher.js](file:///c:/Users/sandh/OneDrive/Documents/exspenso/Desktop/ShipSync/backend/src/services/fuzzyMatcher.js)
- Normalizes names by stripping suffixes (`Pvt Ltd`, `Co.`, `Company`, `Limited`).
- Employs fuzzy matching (Levenshtein distance & Jaccard token index) to group variations.
- Maintains a list of aliases mapped to main parent company names.

#### [NEW] [excelService.js](file:///c:/Users/sandh/OneDrive/Documents/exspenso/Desktop/ShipSync/backend/src/services/excelService.js)
- Reads uploaded Master Excel via SheetJS (`xlsx`) or `exceljs`.
- Separates entries by company.
- Generates custom, stylized Excel sheets (using `exceljs` for borders, header colors, autofitted columns) for each company.
- Wraps them in ZIP or serves direct download links.

#### [NEW] [ocrService.js](file:///c:/Users/sandh/OneDrive/Documents/exspenso/Desktop/ShipSync/backend/src/services/ocrService.js)
- Feeds parcel slip images into Tesseract.js.
- Extracts texts and applies regex pattern matching to parse:
  - Consignment numbers (e.g., `CN-123456789`, `REF-xxxx`)
  - Date (detects varied formats)
  - Weight (extracts digits followed by `kg`, `g`, `lbs`)
  - Destination/Pincodes
  - Company Names
- Returns structured JSON to the frontend.

#### [NEW] [billingService.js](file:///c:/Users/sandh/OneDrive/Documents/exspenso/Desktop/ShipSync/backend/src/services/billingService.js)
- Reads active Weight Slabs and Destination Zones.
- Calculates cost: `Base Price + Excess Weight Rate * Excess Slabs + Zone Surcharge`.
- Adds 18% GST (or customized rate) automatically.
- Computes final billing summary.

